      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the subframe has been reinforced to address chassis fatigue, and the suspension geometry is sharpened with polyurethane bushings and adjustable coilovers. Recent proactive maintenance includes a comprehensive valve lash adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the engine's internal tolerances are within factory specifications. This example offers a balanced compression profile and a rigid, communicative chassis ready for spirited technical driving.",
